Package org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.api.jmx

Interface RepositoryStatsMBean

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RepositoryStats
    @ProviderType
public interface RepositoryStatsMBean
    MBean for providing repository wide statistics. This MBean exposes the time series provided by org.apache.jackrabbit.api.stats.RepositoryStatistics RepositoryStatistics through JMX as CompositeData of arrays.
